                                    </mrow>
                                  </mfrac>
                                  <mo>,</mo>
                                </mrow>
                              </annotation-xml>
                            </semantics>
                          </math> the value of Planck’s constant divided by 2
                          <em data-effect="italics">π</em>).
                        </p>
                        <div data-type="equation" id="fs-idm168356880">
                          <math display="block">
                            <semantics>
                              <mrow>
                                <mrow>
